[ul]Perfect Switching (Perfect For PvP) Decent Eco/Drop Rates Xp rates are currently x675 Working Party Room (Currently Disabled To Improve It) Awesome Donator Benefits Friendly Community & Staff 614 Items 602 Npc Loading Partial 508 maps (fally party room) No Overpowered weapons Clan dicing Loyalty titles Some 508+ Interfaces 562 gameframe (one of a kind) Amazing shops One of a kind Dungeoneering system (Also disabled to improve it a bit, Released date set for June 5th) Bossing (Nomad, Kbd, KQ, Corporal Beast, Sea Troll Queen) All correct Npc attack and dead animations for spawned npcs Clipped following Tree stumps, custom agility, rune essence mining.
